<p>In 2024, e-payments crossed the <a href="https://nibss-plc.com.ng/industry-stat/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">₦1 quadrillion</a> ($736.14 billion) mark. According to<a href="https://informalreport.moniepoint.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">  Moniepoint’s 2025 Informal Economy Report</a>, only one in four informal businesses reported that digital payments accounted for at least 10% of their total revenue in 2025.</p>



