                <p style="padding:5px 0;font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;font-size: 14px;line-height:21px;font-style:italic;letter-spacing:-0.308px;margin-top:0">Fincra connects your business to Africa&#8217;s payment rails without building market by market. For collection, payout, FX, and settlement through a single integration. <a href="https://blog.fincra.com/fincra-canada-psp-license-africa-payments/" style="text-decoration: underline;color: #b61313 !important">See what this means for your business</a>.</p>

